for F being Field
for p being Polynomial of F
for q being non zero Polynomial of F
for s being monic Polynomial of F
holds s = p gcd q iff
      (s divides p & s divides q &
       for r being Polynomial of F st r divides p & r divides q
       holds r divides s);

